# Maestro Dashboard — Production env
#
# Custom domain Appwrite-hoz, hogy a session cookie first-party legyen
# (Safari ITP + Chrome 3rd-party cookie phaseout védelem).
# A CNAME az Appwrite Cloud infra-ra mutat (api.maestro.emago.hu → *.appwrite.global).
VITE_APPWRITE_ENDPOINT=https://api.maestro.emago.hu/v1
